Name: Magnum
Design: The Magnum is based on the first generation of the Dodge Charger Daytona introduced in 1969.

Name: Jager
Design: The Jager is mostly based on the second generation of the Volkswagen Golf introduced in 1983. The front and rear lights resemble ones from the Lancia Delta HF.

Name: Starline
Design: The Starline is based on the tenth generation of the Nissan Skyline introduced in 1998.

Name: Kagura SX
Design: The Kagura SX is based on the seventh generation of the Mitsubishi Lancer Evolution VII introduced in 2001.

Name: Moon MK1
Design: The Moon Mk1 is based on the second generation of the Mitsubishi Eclipse introduced in 1994.

Name: Supernova
Design: The Supernova is based on the third generation of the Chevrolet Chevy II Nova Coupe introduced in 1967.

Name: Tamago
Design: The Tamago is based on the sixth generation of the Honda Civic Hatchback introduced in 1991.
